OL,3,CTwo men appear in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder after human remains found in
OL,5,CSalford
OL,7,FTwo men have appeared in court after
OL,8,Fbeing charged with the murder of a man
OL,9,Fwhose remains were found in woodland
OL,10,Fin Salford.
OL,12,FDiscoveries of body parts were made at
OL,13,FKersal Dale, Blackleach Reservoir and
OL,14,FColliery Wood, all in Salford, over
OL,15,Fthe past three weeks. The first
OL,16,Fdiscovery was on 4 April.
OL,18,Fbelieve the victim was a man in his
OL,19,F60s from Salford.
