OL,3,CTwo men appear in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder after human remains found in
OL,5,CSalford
OL,7,FMichal Jaroslaw Polchowski, 70, and
OL,8,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, both of
OL,9,FWorsley Road, Eccles, have been
OL,10,Fcharged with murder.
OL,12,FThey appeared at Tameside Magistrates
OL,13,FCourt on Monday, with the help of
OL,14,FPolish translators for a three minute
OL,15,Fhearing.
OL,17,FDressed in grey prison-issue
OL,18,Ftracksuits, they spoke only to confirm
OL,19,Ftheir names and dates of birth.
