OL,7,FThe court clerk read out the charge
OL,8,Fthat they are accused of the murder of
OL,9,Fa "person unknown" between March 25
OL,10,Fand April 2.
OL,12,FPolice are in touch with the family of
OL,13,Fthe deceased but formal identification
OL,14,Fhas yet to take place.
OL,16,FGareth Hughes, prosecuting, said the
OL,17,Fmurder charge could only be dealt with
OL,18,Fat a higher court.
