OL,7,FChairman of the bench Trevor Hulmes
OL,8,Ftold the defendants: "You will be
OL,9,Fremanded into custody and be produced
OL,10,Fat the crown court at Manchester Crown
OL,11,FSquare at 9.30am tomorrow."
OL,13,FFormal identification is ongoing. The
OL,14,Fremains that were found at the other
OL,15,Fthree locations are still being tested.
OL,17,FPolice say they are 'confident' they
OL,18,Fbelong to the same victim.
