OL,7,FACC Sarah Jackson said, "We have had
OL,8,Flarge numbers of officers, staff and
OL,9,Fspecialists working diligently on this
OL,10,Finvestigation over the last three
OL,11,Fweeks. It has been very much a large,
OL,12,Fcollective effort, with the victim and
OL,13,Ffamily at the heart of it from the
OL,14,Foutset.
