OL,7,F"We have specially trained officers
OL,8,Fdeployed to support the family as they
OL,9,Fcome to terms with this tragic news.
OL,10,FThey are aware of this morning's
OL,11,Ffurther discovery and will continue to
OL,12,Fbe kept up to date with how we are
OL,13,Fprogressing.
OL,15,F"Despite the charges brought today,
OL,16,Four work is far from over.
