OL,7,F"The scenes we already have
OL,8,Festablished in Bury and Salford will
OL,9,Fremain in place for much of this week
OL,10,Fwhilst our searches and enquiries
OL,11,Fcontinue. Local officers will continue
OL,12,Fto patrol the impacted areas to
OL,13,Fprovide reassurance.
OL,15,F"We will continue following every line
OL,16,Fof enquiry to recover and reunite the
OL,17,Fvictim with his family, bringing a
OL,18,Fdignified end to this terrible
OL,19,Fscenario.
